This male member of an [[Vojak's species|unknown species]] was the '''brother''' of [[Vojak]]. A bounty from an unknown source was placed on him around [[6 BBY/Legends|5.5 BBY]]. He was assassinated by the [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin]] [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[C-3PX]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Bonadan/Legends|Bonadan]].<ref name="Droids 3">[[Droids (1994) 3|''Droids'' (1994) 3]]</ref>

His death also lead to the death of his brother Vojak on [[Hosk Station/Legends|Hosk Station]] by the same droid, as Vojak had gone to attempt to avenge his brother's death.<ref name="Droids 3" />

